      <section eId="sec_121">
        <num>121</num>
        <heading>Reports to directors</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_121__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of\nsubdivision one of section one hundred three of this article. A copy of\nsuch report, together with a list of the directors present at such\nmeeting, verified by the affidavit of the officer or officers charged\nwith the duty of preparing and submitting such report shall be filed\nwith the records of the bank or trust company within five business days\nafter such meeting, and be presumptive evidence of the matters therein\nstated.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
